```python
#2. Take two numbers as input and print their sum
number1=int(input("Enter 1st number to add"))
number2=int(input("Enter 2nd number to add"))
print("Sum of the two numbers:",number1 + number2) # prints sum of 1st number and 2nd number from user
```

OUTPUT :Enter 1st number to add 4
        Enter 2nd number to add 3
        Sum of the two numbers: 7
